<F P=102>  LD0802111994 Prague Radiozurnal Radio Network in Czech 1000 
GMT 8 Feb 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD0802111994 </F>
<F P=104>  Prague Radiozurnal Radio Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Czech </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Excerpt] The meeting between Czech President Vaclav Havel 
and Indian Prime Minister Narasimba Rao scheduled to be held in 
Delhi today has not taken place. According to the president's 
spokesman Ladislav Spacek, the reason is the illness which has 
suddenly affected the Indian prime minister. The Czech 
president therefore continued his four-day state visit to India 
by sightseeing in the capital Delhi. [passage omitted] 

</TEXT>

