<H3> <TI>   General: Army Training To Fight in Golan </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  TA0902172394 Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el in Hebrew 1500 GMT 9 Feb 
94 </F>

<F P=103> TA0902172394 </F>
<F P=104>  Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Hebrew </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] The Golani Brigade has completed an exercise in the 
Golan. Our correspondent Karmela Menashe reports that the 
troops simulated expected combat situations in the Golan and 
exercised cooperation between ground forces. 
  After the exercise, Major General Yitzhaq Mordekhay, the 
Northern Command commander, said that Syria continues its 
military buildup, and the IDF [Israel Defense Forces] is aware 
of the danger from that direction. He stressed that the Army is 
training in the Golan and preparing the Golani Brigade and the 
armored forces and artillery systems for every conceivable task. 

</TEXT>

