<F P=102>  NC1302180794 Beirut Voice of Lebanon in Arabic 1715 GMT 13 
Feb 94 </F>

<F P=103> NC1302180794 </F>
<F P=104>  Beirut Voice of Lebanon </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Arabic </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Hizballah Secretary General Shaykh Hasan Nasrallah 
has called for the destruction of Palestinian leader Yasir 
'Arafat and the Palestinian-Israeli agreement, which he 
described as an accord of humiliation. 
