  [Excerpt] The mysterious "Islamic Group" statement warning 
and threatening foreigners in Egypt has drawn many reactions. 
In an exclusive statement to AL-'ARABI, Muslim Brotherhood 
spokesman counselor Ma'mun al-Hudaybi dismissed the statement of 
the so-called Islamic Group as "a stupid statement issued by an 
unenlightened quarter." The statement is unacceptable from all 
