  [Text] Prime Minister Dr. 'Abd-al-Salam al-Majali, 
accompanied by Interior Minister Salamah Hammad, today visited 
the Public Security Directorate. He discussed with Lieutenant 
General 'Abd-al- Rahman al-'Adwan, director of Public Security, 
a number of issues dealing with the needs of the public security 
body and its role in maintaining the security and stability of 
the Jordanian community. 
  Regarding the objectives of the visit, Lt. Gen. al-'Adwan 
said that the prime minister's visit was designed to reassure 
